Continue straight to stay on Şht. Korg. Hulusi Sayın Blv./D260
Continue to follow D260

Turn right onto Elazığ Keban Yolu/Keban Köprüsü/D260
Continue to follow D260
Keep right to stay on Beypınar Sincan Yolu
Take the exit on the left toward Mehmet Habib Soluk Cd.

Turn right onto Zara Suşehri Yolu/İsmet Paşa Cd./D865
Continue to follow Zara Suşehri Yolu/D865
